01-24T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"UK Sports minister Nigel Adams slammed Saracens' behaviour. 'After the highs of England's performances in Japan World Cup, to come back to this, when some of our best rugby players play for this club, it's hugely disappointing,' he said.<br />\n<br />\n'It's absolutely right the Premiership has taken the action that it has taken. Saracens deserve being relegated. They have to take their medicine.'"},{"pid":"c497e9532b547b75d1bc0389d1d9c728b6e01671","tid":1835401,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"下個到曼城"},{"pid":"d3c4f86f1bbab1e98c33bb4fac06be0441a50e38","tid":1835401,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-GEKBwUMdM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2-GEKBwUMdM&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=d9cff64e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-GEKBwUMdM</a><br />\n倫敦打毗俾人炒廿幾分<br />\n有個學麥巴比慶祝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d2ddc200835c782a81dcbe4832e5182a9d6ceb","tid":1835401,"uid":18692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UGAEcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UGAEcd.jpg&h=c3752dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英超宣佈再扣70分<br />\n而家喺-77分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2857d17e4db2f9394299514cc9bb2b5ffd7b9e","tid":1835401,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880ba7c80fd192968c0f12a0f4cb3df618583c60","tid":1835401,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"奴隸兵咁廢<br />\n抵啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"好撚勁喎，係貴啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src